Open bug `microtasks-starved-by-pending-timer` (NOTES.md).  The
process.nextTick runs (it goes through edge's own tickInfo), but the
Promise microtask never runs — same root cause as
`microtask-before-timer.skip`.  Will un-skip when microtask drain is
fixed; at that point this also smokes the nextTick-before-microtask
ordering (NOTES.md "process.nextTick ordering inversion").
